      <title>ABC 报道雇佣青少年农民工后，HelloFresh 倒闭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/hellofresh-falls-after-abc-report-on-use-of-migrant-teen-workers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[此前美国广播公司 (ABC News) 报道称，美国劳工部正在对 HelloFresh SE 进行调查，指控该公司的一家烹饪和包装工厂使用了青少年移民劳工。此后，HelloFresh SE 股价出现 8 月份以来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/hellofresh-falls-after-abc-report-on-use-of-migrant-teen-workers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 09:09:53 GMT</pubDate>
